snippet.title: Sushant KC - Jhyal Bata (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
“Jhyal Bata” is a folk song, but not your typical folk, its SKC folk. Sounds of traditional nepali instruments like Madal and Murchunga compliment the ‘thet’ lyrics and vocal
melodies. Hope you all like this fusion of folk and skc’s style.

snippet.title: Sooraj Hi Chhaon Banke(Hindi)Salaar |Prabhas |Prithviraj |Prashanth Neel |Ravi Basrur |Hombale Films
snippet.description:
Here is the First Single of Salaar- Sooraj Hi Chhaon Banke

From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the First Single of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films.
 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Dec 22, 2023.

Listen to “Sooraj Hi Chhaon Banke (From "Salaar Cease Fire - Hindi") (Hombale Music)” song on your favorite streaming platforms :-

snippet.description:
सपनालाई बिपना बनाएकाहरुको कथा, असम्भवलाई सम्भव बनाएकाहरुको कथा । निराशालाई आशा बनाएकाहरुको कथा । 
शून्यबाट सुरु गर्दै उचाई चुम्ने खुसी र सुखी मान्छेका कथा । आँट र लगनले बुनेका पौरखी कथाहरु : हेर्ने कथामा ‘गरीखानेका कथाहरु’ 
#hernekatha #Garikhane

Garikhaneka Katha 1 
Herne Katha presents "Garikhaneka Kathaharu", stories woven with courage and passion, of those who turned despair into hope. Stories of those who made dreams come true and who made the impossible, possible. 

"Garikhaneka Kathaharu" is produced in partnership with Nepal Rastra Bank.
https://www.nrb.org.np/

👉 Instagram: https://instagram.com/hernekatha

👉 TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@hernekatha

==== Why Herne Katha? ====
People behind Herne Katha spent 15 years of their lives doing journalism. One day they realised the need to tell more beautiful and inspiring stories of people, the real people. 

👀👀👀 Herne Katha 👀👀👀
Herne Katha is a web series produced by Tana Bana Digital in Nepal. We tell stories of people in the format of short documentaries. New episode of Herne Katha is published on  every  alternate Tuesdays (15 days) on YouTube. You can also watch Herne  Katha on Kantipur  Television every Tuesday 6:30 PM.

💌💌💌 Share your Story 💌💌💌 
If you have a story that is suitable for Herne Katha, please do not hesitate to contact us. 

💲💲💲 For Advertisers 💲💲💲 
If you are an advertiser interested in our show please write us an email  hello@hernekatha.com


🎶🎶🎶 For Singers and Musicians 🎶🎶🎶 
If you are an emerging artist or musicians, we need you. We want to feature your creation in our episodes and support you to get noticed by thousands of our audience. 


🎨🎨🎨 For all Creatives 🎨🎨🎨
Have an idea about anything? Anything related to telling people's stories in bold and beautiful style. Share your ideas with us. We love ideas.  


😢😢😢 Sorry 😢😢😢 
We put a lot of effort to create a single episode of Herne Katha. We will be heartbroken if somebody copies and re-uploads our videos. However, we feel good if you share our links or embed our videos on your blog/website.

🔴 You have come this far reading all the description. Now you deserve to subscribe our channel 😀

snippet.title: Salaar Hindi Trailer | Prabhas | Prashanth Neel | Prithviraj|Shruthi|Hombale Films| Vijay Kiragandur
snippet.description:
Please…I…Kindly…Request!🔥
Presenting the Trailer of #SalaarCeaseFire


From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the official Trailer of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films, this Trailer offers a thrilling glimpse into the intense narrative and mind-blowing visuals that await you. 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Dec 22, 2023.

snippet.title: [NP] 2023 PMGC Grand Finals | Day 3 | PUBG MOBILE Global Championship
snippet.description:
2023 PUBG MOBILE Global Championship Grand Finals ko antim din aisakeko cha! Grand Final ko sabai team haru kada mehenat ka sath afno current position ma pugeka chhan: Uniharulai thaha cha, yehi nai ho yo barsa ko Final chance to prove what they are made of. Aaja euta team matra 2023 PMGC Champion hunecha. Day 3 ma kun team Top ma rahera İstanbul, Türkiye ko spectacular stage ma PMGC ko Trophy claim garne cha ta?

Bishwa ko harek kunna bata 16 team jasle prove garne chhan ki they've earned their spot in the Grand Finals, ra 2023 PMGC ko stage ma utrinechan to clash like never before. Tara Euta matra team rahane cha, sab bhanda mathi! Ko sanga cha ta yo raw strength, strategic brilliance, tactical mastery, unyielding motivation, ra unmatched skills, yo throne lai seize gari Championship Title afno banauna and grab the lion's share of the 2023 PMGC prize pool? Brace yourselves for a pulse-pounding saga and be the witness to moments that will be etched in history!

2023 PMGC Grand Finals ko last day December 10 ma hunecha! Tune in to watch the best in action and the best of the best to become the champion!

Try PUBG MOBILE now: https://pubgmobile.live/PMGCLive2023

💰Total Prize Pool: $3,000,000

snippet.title: छाङ्ग्रुदेखि टिङ्कर भन्ज्याङसम्म | Chhangru to Tinkar Pass | Herne Katha EP115 | हेर्ने कथा
snippet.description:
आज हामी ३ हजार २ सय मिटरको छाङ्ग्रुबाट अझै टाढाको गाउँ टिङ्करतिर उक्लिँदैछौं ।अनि ३ हजार ८ सय मिटरको उचाइमा रहेको टिङ्कर गाउँदेखि झन्डै ५ हजार ३ सय मिटरको उचाइमा रहेको नेपाल चीनको सिमाना टिङ्कर भन्ज्याङसम्म पुग्नेछौं । 

#HerneKatha #Tinkar

In our previous episode, we travelled from Darchula’s headquarters to Chhangru village (elevation 3200 meters) near Kalapani. The villagers from Chhangru had one request for the country’s leaders: a trail road. Today, we are journeying even further - to the Tinkar village which sits at 3,800 meters, and then to the Nepal-China border at 5,300m. 

🏆 Sponsored by 🏆

RMC Group - "Building the Nation Together"
Founded in 1992, RMC Group envisions to enrich the life of every citizen in the country. We are the pioneers in the development of the metal industry of Nepal.  https://bit.ly/45rLKp9

🏩 Hospitality Partner 🏩
🏠 Hotel Pauwa - https://www.hotelpauwa.com/

Part 1 is here: https://youtu.be/8k19E7DWcdg

Herne Katha is amazingly proudly independent journalism. We are free from political or corporate influence. If you love our work and believe in our absolute, astonishing and proud independent journalism please consider supporting us (please only support us if you are financially comfortable). 👍👍👍 Follow Herne Katha 👍👍👍
👉 IMDB: https://www.imdb.com/title/tt8103440/
👉 Facebook:  https://facebook.com/hernekatha

👉 Instagram: https://instagram.com/hernekatha
👉 Website: https://hernekatha.com
👉 TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@hernekatha

==== Why Herne Katha? ====
People behind Herne Katha spent 15 years of their lives doing journalism. One day they realised the need to tell more beautiful and inspiring stories of people, the real people. 

👀👀👀 Herne Katha 👀👀👀
Herne Katha is a web series produced by Tana Bana Digital in Nepal. We tell stories of people in the format of short documentaries. New episode of Herne Katha is published on  every  alternate Tuesdays (15 days) on YouTube. You can also watch Herne  Katha on Kantipur  Television every Tuesday 6:30 PM.

💌💌💌 Share your Story 💌💌💌 
If you have a story that is suitable for Herne Katha, please do not hesitate to contact us. 

💲💲💲 For Advertisers 💲💲💲 
If you are an advertiser interested in our show please write us an email  hello@hernekatha.com


🎶🎶🎶 For Singers and Musicians 🎶🎶🎶 
If you are an emerging artist or musicians, we need you. We want to feature your creation in our episodes and support you to get noticed by thousands of our audience. 


🎨🎨🎨 For all Creatives 🎨🎨🎨
Have an idea about anything? Anything related to telling people's stories in bold and beautiful style. Share your ideas with us. We love ideas.  


😢😢😢 Sorry 😢😢😢 
We put a lot of effort to create a single episode of Herne Katha. We will be heartbroken if somebody copies and re-uploads our videos. However, we feel good if you share our links or embed our videos on your blog/website.

🔴 You have come this far reading all the description. Now you deserve to subscribe our channel 😀

de.title: Nettes Mädchen trifft die Familie, die Matt getötet hat
de.description: ”Hallo, das ist der ganze Passant Urkomisch kniff lig Minuten, um dich zum Lachen zu bringen ”Crazy BGM Series” Douyin erster Autor Das Erstellen ist nicht einfach, Plagiate müssen untersucht werden, achten Sie auf Lern routinen! Ich muss es bereuen, es verpasst zu haben! Wenn Sie Raubkopien haben, hinterlassen Sie eine Nachricht, danke für Ihre Unterstützung!”

ja.title: かわいい妹がマット家族に出会った
ja.description: 「こんにちは、ここは通行人です 爆笑整形 分で笑って止まらない 「狂気のBGMシリーズ」のディザトーンの創始者 創作は容易ではなく、模倣は必ず研究し、学習の道に注目しなければならない! 見逃して後悔します。 海賊版があれば、サポートに感謝します。”

my.title: မိတ်ဆွေ မိသားစုကို တွေ့ကြုံ့ပ်
my.description: ”ဟေဗြဲ၊ ဒီမှာသွားသူလုံးက- ပျော်မွေ့ မိနစ်များက သင့်ကို ရယ်စေလိုသည် ”Crazy BGM Series” ဒါပေမဲ့ ဒီ လို ပြော ပြ တယ် ဆို တာ သိ လာ တယ် ။ ဥပမာ ၊ ဒါပေမဲ့ ဆက်ဆံ ရေး အတွက် ကျေးဇူးတင်ပါတယ်။

id.title: Gadis imut itu membunuh keluarga Matt
id.description: ”Haha, ini seluruh orang yang lewat Lucu Menit untuk membuatmu tertawa ”Crazy BGM Series” Dok Tok Penulis Pertama Penciptaan itu tidak mudah, plagiarisme harus diselidiki, perhatikan rutinitas pembelajaran! Hilang pasti menyesal! Jika Anda memiliki salinan bajakan, silakan tinggalkan pesan, terima kasih atas dukungan Anda!”

th.title: สาวน่ารักเจอฆ่าครอบครัวแมตต์
th.description: ”สวัสดีนี่คือผู้สัญจรทั้งหมด เฮฮาและยุ่งยาก ทำให้คุณหัวเราะในไม่กี่นาที ”Crazy BGM Series” ผู้เขียน Douyin คนแรก การสร้างไม่ใช่เรื่องง่ายการลอกเลียนแบบต้องได้รับการตรวจสอบใส่ใจกับกิจวัตรการเรียนรู้! ฉันจะเสียใจถ้าพลาด! หากมีการละเมิดลิขสิทธิ์โปรดฝากข้อความไว้ขอบคุณสำหรับการสนับสนุน!”

es.title: Linda chica se encuentra con la familia Matar a Matt
es.description: ”Hola, aquí está todo el transeúnte Divertido y complicado Te hace reír en minutos Autor pionero de ”Crazy BGM Series” Douyin La creación no es fácil, el plagio debe ser investigado, ¡preste atención a las rutinas de aprendizaje! ¡Te arrepentirás si te lo pierdes! Si hay alguna piratería, deje un mensaje, ¡gracias por su apoyo!”

pt.title: Garota adorável encontra a família Matt
pt.description: ”Olá, aqui está todo o transeunte O riso é complicado Minutos fazem você rir tanto que não pode parar O primeiro autor de ”Crazy BGM Series” A criação não é fácil, o plágio deve ser investigado e as rotinas de aprendizagem devem ser investigadas! Perder definitivamente se arrepende! Se houver pirataria, deixe uma mensagem, obrigado pelo apoio!”

ar.title: فتاة لطيفة تقابل عائلة مات
ar.description: ”مرحبا ، هذا هو المارة مضحك دقيقة واحدة تجعلك تضحك حتى لا تتوقف المؤلف الأول لـ ”Crazy BGM Series” ليس من السهل الخلق ، يجب التحقيق في الانتحال ، والانتباه إلى الروتين! يجب أن تندم على تفويتها! إذا كان لديك قرصنة ، يمكنك ترك رسالة ، شكرًا لك على الدعم!”

ko.title: 귀여운 소녀가 킬 매트 가족을 만난다
ko.description: ”안녕하세요, 여기 전체 통행인이 있습니다. 웃긴 재미 멈출 수 없을 때까지 몇 분 동안 웃습니다. ”미친 BGM 시리즈” Tiktok 크리에이터 창조는 쉽지 않으며, 표절을 조사해야하며, 학습 루틴에주의를 기울여야합니다! 확실히 후회하지 않았다! 불법 복제가 메시지를 남길 수 있다면 지원에 감사드립니다!”

tr.title: Sevimli kız Matt ailesini vuracak
tr.description: ”Merhaba, bu yoldan geçen kişi.” Komik Dakikalar seni güldürüyor ”Çılgın BGM Serisi” nin ilk yazarı Yaratılış kolay değildir, intihal araştırılmalıdır ve öğrenme rutinine dikkat edin! Kaçırdığınız için kesinlikle pişman olun! Korsanlık varsa, mesaj bırakabilirsiniz, desteğiniz için teşekkür ederiz!”

ru.title: Милая девушка встречает семью Мэтта
ru.description: ”Ой, это весь прохожий. Веселый Вы не можете перестать смеяться через минуту. «Сумасшедший BGM Series» Beying Первый автор Создание не легко, плагиат должен быть исследован, и внимание к учебе! Я определенно сожалею об этом! Если есть пиратство, вы можете оставить сообщение, спасибо за вашу поддержку!”

en.title: Cute girl meets Kill Matt family
en.description: ”Hello, here is the whole passer- Funny Funny Minutes make you laugh until you can't stop ”Crazy BGM Series” Tiktok Creator Creation is not easy, plagiarism must be investigated, pay attention to learning routines! Missed certainly regret! If there is piracy can leave a message, thank you for your support!”

ms.title: Gadis comel itu bertemu dengan keluarga Killing Matt
ms.description: ”Helo, inilah seluruh orang yang lewat Lucu dan rumit Beberapa minit membuat anda ketawa sehingga anda tidak dapat berhenti Pengarang pertama ”Crazy BGM Series” Douyin Penciptaan tidak mudah, plagiarisme mesti disiasat, perhatikan rutin pembelajaran! Saya akan menyesal sekiranya saya terlepas! Sekiranya terdapat cetak rompak, tinggalkan mesej, terima kasih atas sokongan anda!”

zh.title: 當可愛妹子碰到殺馬特家族后#shorts
zh.description: ”哈嘍，這裡是整個路人👻 🌟 爆笑整蠱 分分鐘讓你笑到停不下來 “瘋狂的BGM系列” 抖音首創作者 創作不易，抄襲必究，關注學套路！ 錯過肯定後悔！ 如有盜版可留言，感謝支持！”

fr.title: Une jolie fille rencontre la famille qui tue Matt
fr.description: ”Bonjour, voici tout le passant Rire et délicat Cela vous fait rire jusqu'à ce que vous ne puissiez pas vous arrêter Premier auteur de ”Crazy BGM Series” La création n'est pas facile, le plagiat doit être étudié, faites attention aux routines d'apprentissage! Je regrette certainement de manquer! Si vous êtes piraté, laissez un message, merci pour votre soutien! ””

vi.title: Cô gái dễ thương gặp gia đình Matt
vi.description: ”Xin chào, đây là toàn bộ người qua đường Khéo léo vui nhộn Nó khiến bạn cười trong vài phút Tác giả đầu tiên của ”Crazy BGM Series” Douyin Sáng tạo không dễ, đạo văn phải được điều tra, hãy chú ý đến thói quen học tập! Bỏ lỡ chắc chắn sẽ hối hận! Nếu có bất kỳ vi phạm bản quyền, bạn có thể để lại tin nhắn, cảm ơn bạn đã ủng hộ!”

snippet.title: Custody Full Movie | 2023 New Released Hindi Dubbed Movie | Naga Chaitanya, Krithi Shetty, Priyamani
snippet.description:
Here's presenting "CUSTODY" the Hindi Dubbed Version of the Telugu action thriller Film "CUSTODY", starring Naga Chaitanya, Krithi Shetty, Priyamani, Arvind Swamy, Anandhi, R. Sarath Kumar, Jiiva and Sampath Raj in lead roles.    

Movie (Hindi Dubbed):- Custody 
Original Movie Name:- Custody in Telugu 
StarCast:- Naga Chaitanya, Krithi Shetty, Priyamani, Arvind Swamy, Jiiva, R. Sarath Kumar, Sampath Raj, Anandhi
Music:- Yuvan Shankar Raja, Ilaiyaraaja 
Producer:- Srinivasaa Chituri 
Director:- Venkat Prabhu 

Constable Shiva is assigned to escort a witness from police custody to the courtroom. However, he soon learns Shiva that the entire police department wants the witness dead.
